issue.description: A component referenced in the Visual Basic 6.0 project could not be loaded during the upgrade process
Property or method cannot be automatically upgraded due to differences between Visual Basic 6.0 and Visual Basic .NET
Property or method has a new behavior after being upgraded to Visual Basic .NET
Form property ScaleMode is not supported
Event may fire when form is initialized
Couldn't resolve default property of object
Setting an object variable to Nothing does not destroy the object. Object may not be destroyed until it is garbage collected
Function has a new behavior in .NET
Some objects cannot be upgraded. Properties or methods of those objects have been copied into the upgraded code, but they will not compile because the underlying objects were not upgraded
